{"type": "article", "id": 7588, "title": "Bandit9 Bishop 跑车", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-20T07:31:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234814oxlJ78GnLQIwc3Nm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是一款由北京本土的机车改装厂牌 bandit9 公司打造的一款新型限量款跑车，这款跑车由 Honda Supersport 车身作为基本的架构，采用一体式的高钢级车身，配置了 90cc-125cc 引擎，车身可配搭胡桃木，橡木，柚木等材料，配以石英面层的 LED 灯，烟灰色的麂皮座椅，整部车看起来干练简洁但充满细节。这款车将限量9辆。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052348092sPDgp0afj7ryW4u.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.63447433\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234810sNufgjGPAVlIiB4W.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234810TK6UFalMWq0O8StH.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.59168704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234811XBzbwRujg6MtSQLC.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65525672\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234811OVTUZG4CzAkD6u3Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74449878\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234812WintpOzSR